TEXT: The applicant , Mr Aleksandr Nikolayevich Denisov , is a NORP national , who was born in DATE and lives in GPE , the GPE .
The facts of the case , as submitted by the parties , may be summarised as follows .
On DATE ORG ordered the PERSON - owned mine to make an extraordinary grant to the applicant in the amount of ORG by way of compensation for an occupational disability .
On DATE ORG initiated the enforcement proceedings in the case .

On DATE ORG of Justice ( відділ Державної виконавчої служби PERSON міського управління юстиції ) informed the applicant that it had received a writ of execution ( виконавчий лист ) , dated DATE , on DATE and that the total compensation received by the applicant to date had been ORG CARDINAL,CARDINAL .

On DATE ORG of Justice informed the applicant that , in accordance with LAW on execution proceedings ” ( PERSON виконавче провадження ) , extraordinary grants should be paid as a matter of priority , applying the coefficients stipulated in the said PERSON . It further stated that the total compensation received by the applicant to date had been UAH CARDINAL,CARDINAL.CARDINAL .
The judgment was fully enforced in DATE and the enforcement proceedings were discontinued .

On DATE ORG sent the applicant the schedule of payments which had been made . It mentioned that , as from DATE , the applicant had been paid the whole amount of ORG in CARDINAL instalments ( at least once DATE ) .
On DATE the applicant informed the ORG that the full amount awarded by the judgment of DATE had indeed been paid to him .

On DATE the applicant , in response to a strike - out warning letter from the ORG requesting him to submit comments on the ORG 's observations , informed the ORG , without giving any details that he wished to pursue his application .
